name: Pikachu eyeshadow
description:
bright yellow eyeshadow with shimmer.

All my eye shadows are 100% free of oil, talc and alcohol, perfume and dyes. they are all minerals which can be used dry, or wet and also as liners! i provide samples which are 1/8 tsp of product in a small zip lock bag. and full size is a full 5 grams with a sealed shifter.
Please keep in mind that ANY cosmetic product may cause irritation or allergic reaction. since everyone has different skin types please preform a skin test if you have irritations with most products.But also keep in mind mineral makeup is known to be great for the skin.
